@startuml ViewAllBaseCredentials

actor User
participant BaseCredentialController
participant BaseCredentialService
participant DataSource

User -> BaseCredentialController: GET /base-credentials
activate BaseCredentialController

BaseCredentialController -> BaseCredentialService: findAll(pagination, sort, filter)
activate BaseCredentialService

BaseCredentialService -> DataSource: query base credentials with pagination
activate DataSource
DataSource --> BaseCredentialService: paginated credentials
deactivate DataSource

BaseCredentialService --> BaseCredentialController: PaginateObject<BaseCredential>
deactivate BaseCredentialService

BaseCredentialController --> User: HTTP 200 with credentials
deactivate BaseCredentialController

@enduml
